mmm (0.4.0) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * fix bug caused by True == 1 in Python
  * fix Python 3.7 support and Python 3.5 tests support
  * various fixes, improvements & refactoring
  * make build reproducible
  * ignore broken pipe to prevent backtrace w/ head, tail etc.
  * make EXTS configurable, default to video only and add .webm
  * added man page
  * new: --numeric-sort
  * new: alias

